results.name: Continued fraction expansion of sum(n=1..infinity,(-1)^(n+1)/n^n) = integral(x=0..1) x^(x) dx.
maple: sd1 := proc(n) local i, tren; tren := 0: for i from 1 to n do tren := (-1)^(i+1)*(1/i^(i)) + tren: od; RETURN(tren); end: numtheory[cfrac] (sd1(300),150,'quotients');
